  <brief_title>Examining the Effectiveness of Combined Rehabilitation and Botulinum Toxin Injection on Functional Improvement of the Upper Limb After Stroke</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effectiveness of Botulinum Toxin Combined With Upper Limb Rehabilitation on Arm Function</official_title>
